streamlit-password-generator

Just a simple web app to generate random passwords. Built it using Python and Streamlit so I could customize the character pools easily.

## Features
- Set your own password length
- Checkboxes to toggle numbers, symbols, lowercase, and uppercase letters
- "Include All" shortcut if you're lazy and want a mix of everything
- Throws an error message if you try to generate a password with zero boxes checked

## How to run it
First, make sure you have streamlit installed:
```bash
pip install streamlit
```

Then just run the script:
```bash
streamlit run app.py
``'
